(secondQuint)Efficacy and Safety of Dexlansoprazole Modified Release Formulation to Treat Heartburn.

 This is a Phase 3, randomized, double-blind, multicenter, placebo-controlled, 3-arm study with a 4 week treatment period.

 This study will compare the efficacy of daily Dexlansoprazole MR (60 mg and 90 mg) with that of placebo when administered orally as a single daily dose in the morning, before breakfast.

 The study is designed to evaluate symptom relief in subjects with symptomatic non-erosive GERD.

