 The study consists of two periods; a screening period, which will last a minimum of 7 days and a maximum of 21 days, and a treatment period, which will last 4 weeks.

 Because the development plan for Dexlansoprazole MR was revised, the results of 2 identical studies, T-GD04-082 (this posting, NCT00241745) and T-GD04-083 (NCT00251758), were combined and analyzed as a single larger study referred to as study T-GD04-082.

 A total of 908 subjects were included in the combined analysis; 416 subjects were enrolled into Study T-GD04-082 and 492 subjects were enrolled into Study T-GD04-083.

